{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775859588302,"sessionID":"ses_28685e227ffe79cOB9S8Ppa9Kp","part":{"id":"prt_d797ad38d001TZb8RugYUYbDCu","messageID":"msg_d797ac891001L2n8YF5qP7Oysr","sessionID":"ses_28685e227ffe79cOB9S8Ppa9Kp","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/pkg/router/doc.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/pkg/router/doc.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: /*\n2: Copyright 2026 The Volcano Authors.\n3: \n4: Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (the \"License\");\n5: you may not use this file except in compliance with the License.\n6: You may obtain a copy of the License at\n7: \n8:     http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0\n9: \n10: Unless required by applicable law or agreed to in writing, software\n11: distributed under the License is distributed on an \"AS IS\" BASIS,\n12: WITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied.\n13: See the License for the specific language governing permissions and\n14: limitations under the License.\n15: */\n16: \n17: // Package router provides the HTTP reverse proxy core for AgentCube.\n18: //\n19: // The Router serves as the edge gateway for AgentCube, handling all invocation\n20: // traffic from external clients to sandbox instances. It provides:\n21: //\n22: //   - HTTP reverse proxy with request/response streaming\n23: //   - Dynamic route table management for sandbox endpoints\n24: //   - Path prefix stripping and rewriting\n25: //   - Header injection (X-Sandbox-ID, authentication context)\n26: //   - Connection pooling and keep-alive management\n27: //   - Timeout and circuit breaker patterns\n28: //   - WebSocket upgrade support\n29: //   - Basic load balancing across sandbox replicas\n30: //   - Request/response metrics collection\n31: //   - Access logging for audit trail\n32: //\n33: // The router exposes the following endpoints:\n34: //\n35: //   - GET /health/live - Liveness probe\n36: //   - GET /health/ready - Readiness probe\n37: //   - GET/POST /v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/invocations/*path\n38: //   - GET/POST /v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/invocations/*path\n39: //\n40: // Usage:\n41: //\n42: //\tconfig := &router.Config{\n43: //\t    Port: \"8080\",\n44: //\t    MaxConcurrentRequests: 1000,\n45: //\t}\n46: //\tserver, err := router.NewServer(config)\n47: //\tif err != nil {\n48: //\t    log.Fatal(err)\n49: //\t}\n50: //\tif err := server.Start(); err != nil {\n51: //\t    log.Fatal(err)\n52: //\t}\n53: //\n54: // The router integrates with the session store for session resolution and\n55: // the Workload Manager for sandbox creation on cache misses.\n56: package router\n\n(End of file - total 56 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"/*\nCopyright 2026 The Volcano Authors.\n\nLicensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (the \"License\");\nyou may not use this file except in compliance with the License.\nYou may obtain a copy of the License at\n\n    http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0\n\nUnless required by applicable law or agreed to in writing, software\ndistributed under the License is distributed on an \"AS IS\" BASIS,\nWITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied.\nSee the License for the specific language governing permissions and\nlimitations under the License.\n*/\n\n// Package router provides the HTTP reverse proxy core for AgentCube.\n//\n// The Router serves as the edge gateway for AgentCube, handling all invocation\n// traffic from external clients to sandbox instances. It provides:","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/pkg/router/doc.go","time":{"start":1775859588288,"end":1775859588301}}}}
