{"type":"text","timestamp":1775859607018,"sessionID":"ses_28685e227ffe79cOB9S8Ppa9Kp","part":{"id":"prt_d797b23a50012NgZtrXZ2afcfp","messageID":"msg_d797b0f37001bw1gOi5385fp4p","sessionID":"ses_28685e227ffe79cOB9S8Ppa9Kp","type":"text","text":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Let me write the delta-spec.md for AR-010 Router Session Management:","time":{"start":1775859607016,"end":1775859607016}}}
